verse = \lyricmode {
  Then like a shep -- herd he his peo -- ple guid -- ed,
and in the des -- ert they in him con -- fid -- ed.
He led his flock, and with -- out fear they fol -- lowed,
for all their foes the rag -- ing sea had swal -- lowed.
Thus to his ho -- ly land he brought his own,
to hills and dales which his right hand had won.
}
